Main logotype

  • Should be the first choice when representing the PKP brand
  • Horizontal

Column

  • Vertical
  • Use in page footers

Superscript

  • Horizontal
  • Use in page headers , page footers
  • The superscript is used for “satellite” services, such as Docs, School, Publishing Services, Community Forum

Fraction

  • Vertical
  • Use in footers, always on bottom right
  • In-software branding only
